139
00:09:27,651 --> 00:09:31,154
<i>Grabe. Tuso at maingat pa rin tulad noon.</i>

140
00:09:32,155 --> 00:09:37,077
<i>Pinili ni Sekiya ang alanganing lugar</i>
<i>para maging pinaka-gitna ng lawa.</i>

141
